The Oblitercons/Nemesis Enforcer/Scatterblaster:



Dark One, along with the other Oblitercons, received the transmission from 
Wolfgang.

&quot;A perfect chance to test your new powers if there is combat involved.&quot;

&quot;Or if it&#39;s a waste of time?&quot;

&quot;Be quiet, Break---I mean Mortar.&quot;  Dark One sighed, still not used to the 
names.  He opened up a comm. link with Wolfgang.  &quot;This is Dark One, head of 
the Oblitercon gestalt team.  I and my team will meet you.&quot;

The five robots headed for Wolfgang&#39;s position.

---

Nemesis Enforcer paced back and forth in his quarters, troubled by the 
transmission.  He looked to Scatterblaster.  &quot;Scattershot--&quot;

&quot;Scatterblaster!  How many times do -- what is it?  No, I won&#39;t tell him!  
Just shut up!&quot;

&quot;Are...you talking to me?&quot;

&quot;Uhhh...&quot; Scatterblaster looked around and tapped his head.  &quot;Possibly.&quot;

&quot;O...kay.  Anyway, ScatterBLASTER, it seems Wolfgang is back.  That means he 
somehow broke out of his cage and mutinied.  Computer, where is Zardus?&quot;

&quot;ZARDUS IS NOT ONBOARD THE SHIP.&quot;

&quot;Is he dead?&quot;

&quot;NOT AS FAR AS I KNOW.&quot;

&quot;Where the slag is he, Nemesis?  And who&#39;s Wolfgang?&quot;

&quot;He was here before your time.&quot;

&quot;Obviously!&quot; Scatterblaster yelled, jumping up and slamming a foot down.  &quot;If 
he weren&#39;t before my time I wouldn&#39;t have asked!&quot;

&quot;Alright!&quot; Nemesis yelled, shoving Scatterblaster.  But Scatterblaster sent a 
punch and it knocked Nemesis halfway across his own quarters.  &quot;When the slag 
did you get a punch like that?&quot;

&quot;No idea.  So who&#39;s Wolfgang!&quot;

The former co-commander of the Alliance, a voice said in Scatterblaster&#39;s 
head.  &quot;I said shut up!&quot; he yelled in reply.

&quot;Do you want me to tell you or what?&quot;

&quot;Yes!&quot;

&quot;He was co-commander of the Alliance.  When Zardus went out to do something I 
was left in charge and Wolfgang used that time to try and mutiny, but I was 
able to hold him off until Zardus&#39; return and he was imprisoned.  But now 
Zardus is gone again and he&#39;s trying to make himself ruler of an even great 
Alliance!  He must be stopped!&quot;

&quot;Yeeeeessss...First we should find out who&#39;s with him.  Computer, scan the 
area of Wolfgang&#39;s current location.  Who, except him, is with him?&quot;

&quot;UNITS DARK ONE, BREAKDOWN, PYRO, HISS, AND SCAVENGER.&quot; (Computer hasn&#39;t been 
updated :)

&quot;The Oblitercons!  I never trusted those mercenary gestalts!&quot; Nemesis yelled. 
 &quot;Computer, long range scan, report any detection of Zardus.&quot;

&quot;ENERGY SIGNATURE OF ZARDUS DETECTED AT LOCATIONS APHLA-CENTAURI 24, 24&quot;

&quot;Let&#39;s go!&quot;

&quot;But what if Wolfgang has control of the island? Then we might be destroyed 
like swiss cheese in a blender!&quot;

&quot;I know!  It&#39;s a catastrophic event.  We should go to the signature and 
rescue Zardus.&quot;

&quot;For the glory of the Alliance!&quot;

The Alliance will die.

&quot;No it won&#39;t!&quot; Scatterblaster screamed.

&quot;Voices again?&quot;

&quot;Yeah.&quot;

&quot;Yeah, mine stopped.  It&#39;s been real boring every since.&quot; Nemesis said as he 
lead Scatterblaster out of his quarters and headed for the nearest exit.  &quot;I 
really miss them.&quot;
